            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兑美元今日開市報6.8185元兌1美元，較上日收市價微升3點子。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民幣中間價則定於6.8616兌1美元，較上日下調34點子。</p>\n</div>",
